            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Invicto <lb n="2"/>Mythrae <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ael</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Voc<lb break="no" n="4"/>co <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan> XXII <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>rimigeniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf den Nebenseiten je ein Baum dargestellt. Zahlreiche Ligaturen; Z. 6 befindet sich auf der crepido. Z. 2: H der THR-Ligatur auf dem Foto bei Haug - Sixt nicht erkennbar (B): CIMRM: Z. 2: Mithrae; Filtzinger: Z. 2: Mitrae.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography">
